---
import Section from "src/components/Section.astro";
---

<Section id="about" title="About me">
  <div
    class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-y-8 md:text-lg w-full md:max-w-[520px] lg:max-w-[820px]"
  >
    <p>
      I am a 23-year-old <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-light"
        >Web Developer</span
      >
      with a Software Engineering degree from Universidad Catolica Andres Bello.
      During my <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-light"
        >one year of professional experience</span
      >, I have focused on React frameworks, SQL, NoSQL databases, and software
      testing automation.
    </p>
    <p>
      Thriving in collaborative environments, I leverage strong communication
      skills and analytical thinking to innovate user-friendly solutions. As a
      self-taught individual, <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-light"
        >I quickly grasp new technologies</span
      >, aiming to deliver <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-light"
        >high-quality products</span
      > that exceed user expectations.
    </p>
    <button
      type="button"
      id="open-pdf-button"
      class="flex items-center justify-center py-4 bg-purpleDark dark:bg-purpleLight w-40
      h-10 m-auto text-light dark:text-dark font-semibold rounded-xl h-10 md:text-lg"
    >
      Resume
    </button>
  </div>
</Section>

<script>
  const button = document.getElementById("open-pdf-button");

  button.addEventListener("click", () => {
    window.open("/karen-moran-resume.pdf", "_blank");
  });
</script>
